{"Id":498315,"Title":"藏晖斋诗","Dynasty":"明","Author":"释妙声","Context":"易贵含章，诗称养晦。进德以愚，明道若昧。瞻彼曜灵，运无停机。匪息于渊，害恒其晖。君子则之，以恬养志。出处语嘿，弗愆于义。继我显祖，庶免以之。或升或潜，允也其时。其时维何，像季师表。骏奔东南，于今有耀。世殊事往，手泽尚存。天相斯文，佑我后人。于乎小子，思绳厥武。丕若诒谋，无念尔祖。无念尔祖，淑慎其躬。爰作是诗，式铭尔胸。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"d2f6dadeeff68250d32c9e34c79580a6","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6836959,"Sentence":"易贵含章，诗称养晦。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yì guì hán zhāng ，shī chèn yǎng huì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836960,"Sentence":"进德以愚，明道若昧。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jìn dé yi yú ，mǐng dāo rě mèi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836961,"Sentence":"瞻彼曜灵，运无停机。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhān bi yào lǐng ，yùn mó tǐng jī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836962,"Sentence":"匪息于渊，害恒其晖。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fěi xī yú yuān ，hài héng jī huī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836963,"Sentence":"君子则之，以恬养志。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jūn zi zé zhī ，yi tián yǎng zhì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836964,"Sentence":"出处语嘿，弗愆于义。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chū chǔ yǔ hāi ，fú qiān yú yǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836965,"Sentence":"继我显祖，庶免以之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jì wǒ xiǎn zǔ ，shù miǎn yi zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836966,"Sentence":"或升或潜，允也其时。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huò shēng huò qián ，yǔn yě jī shǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836967,"Sentence":"其时维何，像季师表。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jī shǐ wéi hé ，xiàng jì shī biǎo ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6836968,"Sentence":"骏奔东南